@startuml state-password-flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Password Hashing & Rehash Flow

[*] --> PolicyCheck : User submits password

PolicyCheck : PasswordPolicy.validate()
PolicyCheck : check length, complexity,\noptional HIBP breach check

PolicyCheck --> Rejected : violations found
PolicyCheck --> Hashing : policy satisfied

Rejected --> [*] : return violations[]

Hashing : Argon2idHasher.hash()
Hashing : PASSWORD_ARGON2ID algorithm
Hashing : memory-hard, GPU-resistant

Hashing --> Stored : $argon2id$v=19$...

Stored --> [*] : save to DB

note "Login flow" as N1

[*] --> Verify : User logs in
Verify : hasher.verify(plain, storedHash)
Verify --> LoginFailed : hash_equals() = false
Verify --> NeedsRehash : verified OK
LoginFailed --> [*]

NeedsRehash : hasher.needsRehash(storedHash)\ncheck if params changed
NeedsRehash --> RehashAndSave : needs upgrade
NeedsRehash --> LoginSuccess : hash still current

RehashAndSave : hash(plain) with new params
RehashAndSave : update DB transparently
RehashAndSave --> LoginSuccess

LoginSuccess --> [*]

@enduml
